{"tid":1463440,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"民意撚只會將今次既革命(或者民意撚口中既運動)推向失敗","createTime":"2019-08-13T13:03:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-13T15:21:56.000Z","uid":33053,"like":37,"dislike":18,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"98f178012f809ad75707e8926b788521a2dea340","tid":1463440,"uid":33053,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T13:03:59.000Z","msg":"呢班民意撚 成日話入機場同旅客講解香港發生咩事<br />\n喂阿哥 我係旅客聽完 除左講句support u guys<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />, 甚至noted with thanks<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />之外<br />\n佢有咩可以幫到你？<br />\n你地自己諗下<br />\n由69 612 到今日 贏撚左咁多民意 咁又點？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n五大訴求回應左未？政府同黑警當你班香港人係on9仔咋<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n再睇下我地輸左d咩<br />\n六條手足既命，爆左兩隻眼，無數人受傷，被捕，比黑警打<br />\n你地呢班民意撚 拎住民意打完飛機就算？有冇諗過要贏？<br />\n2014年又係和理非話要民意<br />\n結果係點？大家有眼睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b0abd0537c7692270e27403fe7415639a59f5e3b","tid":1463440,"uid":33053,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T13:06:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d263f6eb01b475cb065491f709ad1e4bce55f7e7","tid":1463440,"uid":162272,"like":4,"dislike":6,"score":-2,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T13:13:47.000Z","msg":"無民意全港拍住手送你入監牢"},{"pid":"ad73ee86aa941e39b49cb4db0e5cd6398f1bcea7","tid":1463440,"uid":33736,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"d263f6eb01b475cb065491f709ad1e4bce55f7e7","tid":1463440,"uid":162272,"like":4,"dislike":6,"score":-2,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T13:13:47.000Z","msg":"無民意全港拍住手送你入監牢"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T13:15:57.000Z","msg":"已經有七百手足半隻腳入咗監牢"},{"pid":"79c171eb762f10c7c5fbc5045bb481727cd3ad3c","tid":1463440,"uid":33736,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"ad73ee86aa941e39b49cb4db0e5cd6398f1bcea7","tid":1463440,"uid":33736,"like":6,"dislike":0,"sc